---
title: SuperQuick Chili Fried Egg Bowls with Veggie-Jumbled Rice
description: Eggs for dinner is always a great idea! Our fried eggs feature chilis and sesame seeds, giving our veggie-loaded sesame-scented rice a pop of flavour.

